          <Comment>For these reasons, this variant has been classified as Pathogenic. ClinVar contains an entry for this variant (Variation ID: 14234). This premature translational stop signal has been observed in individual(s) with abetalipoproteinemia (PMID: 8361539). This variant is not present in population databases (gnomAD no frequency). This sequence change creates a premature translational stop signal (p.Pro72Leufs*8) in the MTTP gene. It is expected to result in an absent or disrupted protein product. Loss-of-function variants in MTTP are known to be pathogenic (PMID: 8533758, 9671739).</Comment>
